Tabulature printer webapp

UI shows full sheet of manuscript paper with tabulature staves of six unlabeled lines. Menu button in screen corner. Additional page button at bottom.

User adds alphanumeric fret indicators on the lines and bar lines and repeat signs across them.

Navigation by keyboard or mouse.

Menu options:
landscape/portrait
number of lines per staff
automatic bar lines: 0/4 bars per staff
fret indicator on/above line
Export: PNG (all pages or page 1), print/PDF
